  <name>Grand Old Dukes</name>
  <author>
   <name>Gravelfoyle Events</name>
   <link href="https://www.dukesweekender.com/god"/>
  </author>
  <desc>Grand Old Dukes is 111 miles with 10,000ft of climbing - It’s a big day oot in Gravefoyle! We’ll take you on some absolutely stunning gravel trails via some of our most stunning lochs and glens. There will be short sections of road too but largely quiet and likely a welcome reprieve from the gravel!</desc>
  <link href="https://ridewithgps.com/routes/54512851"/>
  <time>2026-05-31T09:00:00Z</time>
